I thank you, Lord, that you made me new. I ask you to write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

01:48:48.880 --> 01:48:57.616
From this day forward, I'll serve you forevermore. Thank you, Jesus. I believe I'm saved, Lord.

01:48:57.617 --> 01:49:06.165
Amen and amen."If you said that prayer with me and you meant it with your whole heart, I believe you're saved.

01:49:06.166 --> 01:49:13.342
