01:49:13.343 --> 01:49:20.158
But you have to confess it and you have to believe it, saying he is your Lord and Savior.

01:49:20.159 --> 01:49:24.959
And as you do that, I believe you're a born-again Christian.

01:49:24.960 --> 01:49:29.899
Now you say, "What do I do now, Brandon?"Well, you find a Bible-believing church.

01:49:29.900 --> 01:49:39.535
I believe a non-denominational church—that's personally what I would do—and I would get plugged in there.

01:49:39.536 --> 01:49:55.713
Go to church on Sundays and Wednesdays; get plugged in. Tell the pastor there, "I got born again on a YouTube broadcast and I need to be water-baptized.

01:49:55.714 --> 01:50:03.431
