01:50:03.432 --> 01:50:10.603
Find a Bible. Read your Bible every day. Pray. Come pray with us and start a new life.

01:50:10.604 --> 01:50:20.621
This is the Christian walk. Now, if you can't afford a Bible and you say, "Braden, I watched your broadcast. I can't afford a Bible.

01:50:20.622 --> 01:50:26.879
I'm on food stamps and I don't even know if I'm getting food stamps tomorrow, but I'm trusting the Lord's going to take care of me.

01:50:26.880 --> 01:50:32.655
What do I do? How do I get a Bible?"well, my wife and I will buy you your first Bible.

01:50:32.656 --> 01:50:36.606
All you have to do is email us at the address in the description down below.

01:50:36.607 --> 01:50:40.431
We will not solicit your email address. We will not bother you ever again.

01:50:40.432 --> 01:50:53.448
We just want to celebrate your decision tonight. There's an email down below. Email that and put in the heading: "I got born again.

01:50:53.449 --> 01:51:07.217
I would like to have my free Bible."Just give us your address and your name, and we'll send it to you from Amazon just to be a blessing to you, just to tell you congratulations on becoming a new Christian.

01:51:07.218 --> 01:51:16.279
Thank you for joining us, and we rejoice in your decision tonight. My son says there were 49 salvations so far.

01:51:16.280 --> 01:51:24.390
We're so excited for all 49 of you who gave your hearts to Jesus Christ.

01:51:24.391 --> 01:51:30.717
We celebrate your decision. All glory to Jesus. Hallelujah!

01:51:30.718 --> 01:51:39.039
49 newcomers, please stick around and come pray with us. We're excited you're here.

01:51:39.040 --> 01:51:48.971
Tonight was a good night for you to get saved. Any night is a good night to come to Jesus.

01:51:48.972 --> 01:51:54.733
If you could like, subscribe, and comment something down below.

01:51:54.734 --> 01:52:02.874
Braden says 50 new salvations tonight. That's wonderful. I almost didn't give an altar call.

01:52:02.875 --> 01:52:09.824
Shame on me; Lord, forgive me for that. That's terrible. We would have had 50 people born again.

01:52:09.825 --> 01:52:14.734
50 people gave their hearts to Jesus Christ tonight. Thank you, Lord, for your mercy.

01:52:14.735 --> 01:52:23.118
He said, 'Brandon, you need to do this.'I'm so glad he did. I was going to close it before I even had one.

01:52:23.119 --> 01:52:27.363
He's such a good God. He knew 50 people would come to Jesus tonight.

01:52:27.364 --> 01:52:36.472
Isn't that wonderful? He's ready to have a big old party. He's excited about your decision.

01:52:36.473 --> 01:52:49.146
He's going, 'Woo-hoo!'It's exciting. Well, like I said, it was a bit different tonight, but I pray it blessed you.

01:52:49.147 --> 01:52:59.517
I pray the Lord is stirring in you. You feel stirred. You want to have a relationship with the Father.

01:52:59.518 --> 01:53:10.319
He wants a friendship with you so bad. He said to me, 'I'm looking for a friend.

