I want a friend tonight.'I said, 'The creator of heaven and earth, the creator of the universe, the creator who created everything is looking for a friend.

01:53:27.840 --> 01:53:39.039
He wants an intimate relationship with me and with you. What is man that you are mindful of him?

01:53:39.040 --> 01:53:46.043
Like David said, "What is man?"He's looking for intimacy. He wants a friend.

01:53:46.044 --> 01:53:59.913
Be my Father's friend. It's not religious; it's intimacy. So many people are all about religion.

01:53:59.914 --> 01:54:06.319
No, I cannot stand religion. I love Jesus. It's a relationship.

01:54:06.320 --> 01:54:15.990
Whatever denomination you pick, I want Jesus. I'm non-denominational.

01:54:15.991 --> 01:54:24.399
I don't claim a denomination; I claim Jesus. Help me, Father, to be more intimate with you tonight.

01:54:24.400 --> 01:55:08.959
Thank you, Father. All glory. We give all of the glory to Jesus and tell of his wonderful love.

01:55:08.960 --> 01:55:16.564
Glory to God. Well, thank you for joining us tonight. We pray it blessed you and we'll see you again tomorrow.

01:55:16.565 --> 01:55:27.641
We've got confetti! They got saved; we've got confetti! It's a party.

01:55:27.642 --> 01:55:35.378
